object.script:
gen1=0 gen2=0 t=0 totalGen=0
function Clamp(val, min, max) return math.min(math.max(val, min), max) end
function sc(r,g,b) screen.setColor(r,g,b) end
function dr(x,y,w,h) screen.drawRectF(x,y,w,h) end
function dl(x1,y1,x2,y2) screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end
function dt(x,y,tx) screen.drawText(x,y,tx) end
function onTick() gen1 = input.getNumber(1) gen2 = input.getNumber(2) totalGen=gen1+gen2
end
function spin(x,y)
if (t<1) then dl(x,y,x,y-4) end
if (t>=1) and (t<2) then dl(x,y,x+3,y-3) end
if (t>=2) and (t<3) then dl(x,y,x+4,y) end
if (t>=3) and (t<4) then dl(x,y,x+3,y+3) end
if (t>=4) and (t<5) then dl(x,y,x,y+4) end
if (t>=5) and (t<6) then dl(x,y,x-4,y+3) end
if (t>=6) and (t<7) then dl(x,y,x-4,y) end
if (t>=7) then dl(x,y,x-3,y-3) end
end
function onDraw() sc(30,30,30) dr(0,0,31,31) sc(5,5,5)
dr(0,0,31,7) sc(30,30,30) dt(1,1,"OUTPUT") sc(5,5,5)
dt(15,11,math.ceil(gen1)) dt(15,22,math.ceil(gen2))
screen.drawCircle(7,13,4) screen.drawCircle(7,24,4)
spin(7,13) spin(7,24)
if (t>=7) then t=0 else t=t+(totalGen/223.12) end
end

piston = 0.2 t=0
function clamp(val, min, max) return math.min(math.max(val, min), max) end
function onTick()
up = input.getBool(1) down = input.getBool(3)
if t>5 then
if up then piston=clamp(piston+0.02,-0.5,0.5) end
if down then piston=clamp(piston-0.02,-0.5,0.5) end t=0 end
t=t+1 if t>10000 then --prevent overflow t=0 end
output.setNumber(5, piston)
end

d=0 open=false pivot=0
function onTick()
b1 = input.getBool(1) b2 = input.getBool(2) red=0 green=0 blue=0
if ((b1 or b2) and (d>60)) then open=not open d=0 end d=d+1
if (d>100000) then d=0 end
if open then pivot=1 else pivot=0 end
if open then blue=100 end
output.setNumber(1,red) output.setNumber(2,green) output.setNumber(3,blue) output.setNumber(5,pivot)
end

s=0 t=0 oldBat=0 inBat=0 rate=0 currentMenu=1 click=0 fMax=60 f=0 ovMode=false outFuel=0 inFuel=0 outClutch=0 MAXTH=0.375 SUPERTH=0.525 inSuper=false highTemp=false
function Clamp(val, min, max) return math.min(math.max(val, min), max) end function sc(r,g,b) screen.setColor(r,g,b) end function dr(x,y,w,h) screen.drawRectF(x,y,w,h) end function dl(x1,y1,x2,y2) screen.drawLine(x1,y1,x2,y2) end function dt(x,y,tx) screen.drawText(x,y,tx) end
function GetTHJump() if (rate<0) then if (math.abs(rate)>=0.005) then return 0.05 else return 0.01 end else if (math.abs(rate)>=0.005) then return 0.05 else if inBat==1 then return 0.01 else return 0 end end end end
function onTick() inMain = input.getBool(1) inTemp = input.getNumber(2) inRPS = input.getNumber(3) inFuel = input.getNumber(6) inBat = input.getNumber(8) inX = input.getNumber(9) inY = input.getNumber(10) isPressed = input.getBool(11) inKey = input.getBool(12) inSuper = input.getBool(13)
outStarter = (inMain and inKey and (inRPS<=6) and (inFuel>0.5)) outRunning = (inRPS >= 6) outBuzz=false if (inMain and inKey) then if (not outRunning) then outFuel = 0.12 oldBat=inBat s=0 t=0 outClutch=0 else if (inTemp>99) then highTemp=true end if (s>=60) then outClutch=Clamp(outClutch+0.017,0,1) else s=s+1 end rate = inBat-oldBat if (t>180) then
if ((inRPS>=20) and (rate<0) and (inBat<0.4) and not(inSuper)) then ovMode=true else ovMode=false end
if inSuper then if highTemp then outFuel=MAXTH if inTemp<=90 then highTemp=false end else outFuel=SUPERTH end else if (inBat<0.5) then outFuel = MAXTH else if (inBat<oldBat) then outFuel = Clamp(outFuel+GetTHJump(),0.1325,MAXTH) else outFuel = Clamp(outFuel-GetTHJump(),0.1325,MAXTH) end end end oldBat=inBat t=0 end end outAir = outFuel * 2 t=t+1 if ((f==0) and ovMode) then outBuzz=true end flashDelay() else outFuel = 0 outClutch = 0 s=0 t=0 end
output.setBool(1, outStarter) output.setBool(2, outRunning) output.setNumber(3, outFuel) output.setNumber(4, outAir) output.setBool(5, outBuzz) output.setNumber(6, outClutch) end
function flashDelay() if (f>=fMax) then f=0 else f=f+1 end end
function pixPosL(n) if (n>=100) then return 8 else if (n<10) then return 18 else return 13 end end end
function pixPosR(n) if (n>=100) then return 40 else if (n<10) then return 50 else return 45 end end end
function onDraw() display() if ovMode then dispSpecial(0) else if inSuper then if highTemp then dispSpecial(1) else dispSpecial(2) end end end end
function display() sc(30,30,30) dr(0,0,64,64) sc(5,5,5) dr(0,0,64,7) sc(30,30,30) dt(10,1,"FRAGField") sc(5,5,5)
dt(22,8,"3500") dl(1,8,20,8) dl(1,10,15,10) dl(1,12,10,12)
dl(43,8,63,8) dl(48,10,63,10) dl(53,12,63,12)
dt(3, 16, "power") dt(41, 16, "fuel") dt(3,30,"RPS") dt(41, 30, "TEMP") dt(3,44,"BATT") dt(41,44,"RATE")
sc(8,8,8)
rpsPerc = math.floor(inRPS/21.49*100) dt(pixPosL(rpsPerc),22,rpsPerc.."%")
fuelPerc = math.ceil(inFuel/1484.375*100) dt(pixPosR(fuelPerc),22,Clamp(fuelPerc,0,100).."%")
dt(pixPosL(math.floor(inRPS)),36,math.floor(inRPS))
dt(pixPosR(math.ceil(inTemp)),36,math.ceil(inTemp).."c")
batPerc = math.ceil(inBat*100) dt(pixPosL(batPerc),50,math.ceil(batPerc).."%")
if (inBat>=1) then dt(43,50,"---") else if (f<30) then sc(30,30,30) end if (rate>=0) then dl(50,50,50,55) dl(50,50,53,53) dl(50,50,47,53) else dl(50,50,50,55) dl(50,55,53,52) dl(50,55,47,52) end end end
function dispSpecial(i) if (f<30) then sc(30,30,30) dr(0,57,64,7) else sc(5,5,5) dr(0,57,64,7) sc(30,30,30) if i==0 then dt(12,58,"OVERLOAD") else if i==1 then dt(14,58,"COOLING") else dt(4,58, "SUPERCHARGE") end end end
end
